---
import Layout from '../../components/layout/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Business Automation Services - Isaac Benyakar"
  description="Transform your business operations with intelligent automation solutions that save time, reduce costs, and eliminate manual processes."
>
  <div class="pt-8">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-purple-900 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Business Automation
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Eliminate manual processes and build systems that work 24/7 to grow your business while you focus on what matters most.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/contact"
            class="bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            Automate Your Business
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <section class="bg-slate-800 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
              Why Automation Transforms Businesses
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
              Based on 7+ years of building successful automation systems
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-green-400 font-mono">◉</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-400">Save 20+ Hours Weekly</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Eliminate repetitive tasks and let intelligent systems handle routine operations so your team can focus on growth.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-blue-400 font-mono">◉</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">Reduce Operational Costs</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Cut labor costs and eliminate human errors that lead to expensive mistakes and customer dissatisfaction.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-xl text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-purple-400 font-mono">◉</div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-400">Scale Without Hiring</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Handle 3x more volume without additional staff by automating workflows and optimizing processes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-16 text-center text-white">Automation Solutions I Provide</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl mr-6 mt-2 text-blue-400 font-mono">↻</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-blue-400">Workflow Automation</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                    Automate complex business processes from lead capture to customer onboarding, invoicing, and follow-ups.
                  </p>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <div>• Email marketing automation</div>
                    <div>• Lead nurturing sequences</div>
                    <div>• Invoice generation & payment processing</div>
                    <div>• Customer onboarding workflows</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl mr-6 mt-2 text-green-400 font-mono">▢</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-green-400">Data Processing & Analytics</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                    Transform raw data into actionable insights with automated reporting, data collection, and analysis systems.
                  </p>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <div>• Automated report generation</div>
                    <div>• Data collection from multiple sources</div>
                    <div>• Real-time dashboards</div>
                    <div>• Performance monitoring alerts</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl mr-6 mt-2 text-purple-400 font-mono">▧</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-purple-400">E-commerce Automation</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                    Streamline your online store operations with inventory management, order processing, and customer communication automation.
                  </p>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <div>• Inventory synchronization</div>
                    <div>• Order fulfillment automation</div>
                    <div>• Price monitoring & optimization</div>
                    <div>• Customer service chatbots</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-800 p-8 rounded-xl">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="text-3xl mr-6 mt-2 text-orange-400 font-mono">⧈</div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-orange-400">API Integrations</h3>
                  <p class="text-slate-300 mb-4">
                    Connect your existing tools and systems to work together seamlessly with custom API integrations and middleware.
                  </p>
                  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
                    <div>• CRM & marketing tool integrations</div>
                    <div>• Payment processor connections</div>
                    <div>• Third-party service automation</div>
                    <div>• Custom webhook development</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Success Story -->
    <section class="bg-slate-800 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Real Automation Success</h2>
          <div class="bg-slate-700 p-8 rounded-xl">
            <div class="text-6xl mb-6 text-purple-400 font-mono">↗</div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-400">Restocktime: 7 Years of Automation Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 text-lg">
              My own automation business processes 1,000+ notifications daily, serves 8,971 followers, 
              and maintains 99.9% uptime—all running automatically for over 7 years.
            </p>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">7+</div>
                <div class="text-slate-300">Years Operating</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-400">1K+</div>
                <div class="text-slate-300">Daily Automations</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-400">99.9%</div>
                <div class="text-slate-300">Uptime</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a 
              href="/projects/restocktime"
              class="inline-block mt-6 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
            >
              See Full Case Study
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-blue-600 py-20">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Ready to Automate Your Success?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-purple-100 mb-8">
          Let's identify the biggest time-wasters in your business and build systems that eliminate them forever.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/contact"
          class="bg-white text-purple-600 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-purple-50 transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule Automation Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>